         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">14/6/76 ¶  ¶ Would you have the kindness, dear Mr Ramsay, to send me a copy of each of the school books, adopted at the State Schools, so that I may see, how far their form can be adopted for the inte...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">76.06.14a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Robert Ramsay</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">76/21348, unit 328, VPRS 794 central inwards registered correspondence, VA 714 Education Department, Public Record Office, Victoria.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; "/>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>MS black-edged; M's brother-in-law, Eduard Wehl, had died on 11 February 1876.</p>
               </note>14/6/76</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Would you have the kindness, dear Mr Ramsay, to send me a copy of each of the school books, adopted at the State Schools, so that I may see, how far their form can be adopted for the intended school flora.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>On 21 June 1876 Ramsay minuted: 'Forward copies'.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>A further annotation explains: 'i.e.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Reading books from<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>2nd upwards'.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>On 27 June,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>the file was annotated:<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>'copies of<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>2d, 3d, 4th &amp; 5th Reading books<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>sent with<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>letter [SB]<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>76/109'<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">.</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">Publication of the<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>'school flora'<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>was<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">stopped by John MacPherson, Ramsay's successor as Chief Secretary when the Government changed on 20 October 1875. See discussion in Lucas<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">et al.</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>(2006), pp. 37-39.</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">With best respects</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd von Mueller</p>
         </div>
      </body>
   </text>
